eed are unmatched. " Alex Chen AI Researcher, Stanford " Finally, an API that just works. No approval hassles, no rate limit nightmares. Pure gold. " Sarah Johnson CTO, DataInsights " Built my entire startup on TwitterAPI.io. The cost savings compared to alternatives are incredible. " Marcus Liu Indie Developer Built for Scale, Priced for Everyone Lightning Fast Average response time under 500ms with global CDN Ridiculously Affordable 100x cheaper than official API Enterprise Reliable 99.99% uptime SLA with automatic failover Global Infrastructure Servers in 12+ regions for lowest latency Real-time Streams WebSocket and webhook support for live data Auto-scaling Handles traffic spikes without breaking a sweat Frequently Asked Questions Everything you need to know about TwitterAPI.io What is TwitterAPI.io? ▼ TwitterAPI.io is a developer-friendly alternative to Twitter's official API, giving you real-time and historical tweet data plus write actions (posting, liking, etc.) at a fraction of the cost. Is it X or Twitter? ▼ X is the new name for Twitter (rebranded in 2023). It's the same platform; we say 'X (formerly Twitter)' so developers who still search for 'Twitter API' can find us. How do I use TwitterAPI.io? ▼ Simply create a free account, copy your API key, and start calling our REST or WebSocket endpoints. Swagger docs, a Postman collection, and ready-to-paste code snippets make integration painless. Do I need a Twitter developer account? ▼ No! TwitterAPI.io bypasses the need for Twitter's approval process. Start immediately with just an API key. How does pricing work? ▼ Simple pay-as-you-go: $0.15 per 1,000 tweets, $0.18 per 1,000 profiles. No monthly fees, no hidden costs. What's your rate limit? ▼ We support 1000+ requests per second by default. Need more? Contact us for custom enterprise limits. How fresh is your data? ▼ Real-time. Our data is updated continuously with sub-second latency from Twitter's firehose. Can I try it risk-free? ▼ Get $0.1 in free credits immediately - no credit card required to start. What about support? ▼ 24/7 live chat support, comprehensive docs, and dedicated account managers for enterprise customers. Do you offer academic discounts for students and researchers? ▼ Yes! We're committed to supporting education and academic research. We offer special academic pricing for students, faculty, and research institutions. Please email us at hello@twitterapi.io with your .edu email address and a brief description of your research project to apply for our academic discount program. twitterapi.io Enterprise-grade public data API that powers your decision-making with real-time social intelligence. Social Responsibility 🌱 Stripe Climate Commitment We donate a portion of every sale to fund carbon removal technologies.

